Description: LibriSpeech WER and RTF benchmark for rkwhisperd
 Command-line tool that runs rkwhisperd against LibriSpeech test-clean and
 test-other splits, reporting word error rate (WER) and real-time factor
 (RTF) per utterance and as a corpus-level summary.
